---
pagination:
  data: blog
  size: 1
  alias: article
permalink: "/blog/{{ article.slug }}/"
layout: base.njk
eleventyComputed:
  title: "{{ article.title }} | Blog Möxer"
  description: "{{ article.excerpt }}"
---

<section class="page-hero" style="padding-bottom:2rem;">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/blog/" class="article-back">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="14" height="14"><path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/></svg>
      Volver al blog
    </a>
    <span class="page-hero__label">{{ article.category }}</span>
    <h1 class="page-hero__title" style="max-width:20ch; margin-inline:auto;">{{ article.title }}</h1>
    <p class="page-hero__subtitle">{{ article.readTime }} min de lectura</p>
    <img
      src="{{ article.image }}"
      alt="{{ article.title }}"
      class="article-hero__image"
      loading="eager"
    >
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top:3rem;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="article-content">
      {{ article.content | safe }}
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:3rem; text-align:center;">
      <a href="/blog/" class="btn btn--outline-green">← Volver al blog</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="cta-section__kicker">¿Dudas sobre qué modelo elegir?</span>
    <h2 class="cta-section__title" style="max-width:18ch; margin-inline:auto;">Tu óptico conoce Möxer</h2>
    <p class="cta-section__text">En tu óptica de confianza encontrarás los modelos Möxer y el asesoramiento profesional para elegir el ideal para ti.</p>
    <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content:center;">
      <a href="/donde-comprar/" class="btn btn--primary btn--large">Encontrar óptica</a>
      <a href="/colecciones/" class="btn btn--outline btn--large">Ver colecciones</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
